73 There is Romena there, where I forged  
74 the sealed bond of the Baptist;  
75 so that I left the body burnt up.

88 I am for them among such made family;  
89 and they induced me to beat the fiorini  
90 that had three carats of mondiglia.

97 The one is the false one that Joseph accused;  
98 the other is the false Sinon Greek of Troy:  
99 by acute fever they throw so much leppo.

109 Whereupon he answered: “When you were going  
110 to the fire, you had not it so soon;  
111 but yes and more I had it when you were forging”.

118 “Remember, perjurer, the horse,”  
119 answered he who had infused the epa;  
120 “and may you be guilty that the whole world may know!”

142 «Greater defect less shame washes»,  
143 said the master, «that yours has not been;  
144 however of every wretchedness it burdens you.
